         <abstract>
            <p>Various triangular finite C&lt;sup&gt;0&lt;/sup&gt;-elements of Hermite type satisfying the maximum-angle condition are presented and corresponding finite element interpolation theorems are proved. The paper contains also a proof that very general hypotheses due to Jamet are not necessary for such finite elements.</p>
          </abstract>
